snippet.title: Prototype N Demo (2022) Trailer NOW AVAILABLE!
snippet.description:
The new demo is now available at SAGExpo!
You can find it at:

Itch.io Page: https://arrietty.itch.io/prototype-n
SAGExpo booth Page: https://sonicfangameshq.com/forums/showcase/prototype-n-sage-2022-demo.1417/

Visit the SAGExpo site for more games by other cool creators: https://sagexpo.org/

Destructive robots are running rampant across the world! Nadine, an incomplete prototype robot of unknown origin, fights to save the world while searching for her creator.

This demo contains 7 levels across 3 worlds, filled with obstables and enemies. Use your weapons you find around the levels to overcome them and find secrets!
